0144/http://matthewg.org/papers/ideologicalright.pdf}}<br>{{Cite journal|title=|author=|url=http://faculty.washington.edu/jwilker/353/AbramowitzTea.pdf|journal=|language=en|access-date=2022-01-21|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524131511/https://faculty.washington.edu/jwilker/353/AbramowitzTea.pdf}}<br>{{Cite journal|title=|author=|url=http://www.stat.columbia.edu/~gelman/research/published/reversal2.pdf|journal=|language=en|access-date=2022-01-21|archive-date=2021-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227214652/http://www.stat.columbia.edu/~gelman/research/published/reversal2.pdf}}<br>{{Cite web|url=https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/special/news_seminar/jiji/jiji46/|title=１からわかる！トランプ再選は？（２）挑戦者は誰？|publisher=NHK|accessdate=2020-12-22|archive-date=2022-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205041529/https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/special/news_seminar/jiji/jiji46/}}</ref><br>'''派系：'''<br>[[中間偏右|中間偏右]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Republican Governance Group|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Republican_Governance_Group&oldid=1065900990|date=2022-01-15|journal=Wikipedia|language=en|access-date=2022-01-21|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421190116/https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Republican_Governance_Group&oldid=1065900990}}</ref><ref name="auto1">{{cite news|last=Siegel|first=Josh|title=Centrist Republicans and Democrats meet to devise bipartisan healthcare plan|url=https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/centrist-republicans-and-democrats-meet-to-devise-bipartisan-healthcare-plan|work=[[The_Washington_Examiner|The Washington Examiner]]|date=2017-07-18|access-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505135032/https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/centrist-republicans-and-democrats-meet-to-devise-bipartisan-healthcare-plan|archive-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>至[[極右翼|極右翼]]<ref>{{cita web|url=https://apnews.com/article/noticias-be0fc58f73e2f60a7f6363ae6a0bc0ff|title=Republicanos hacen las paces con la extrema derecha|date=2021-02-05|author=Steve Peoples|website=[[Associated_Press|AP News]]|location=Nueva York|access-date=2022-01-21|archive-date=2022-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421190119/https://apnews.com/article/noticias-be0fc58f73e2f60a7f6363ae6a0bc0ff}}</ref>
